channel.name: X12: Parsing and Generation
channel.description:
This shows a simple example of parsing and generating an X12 transaction using Iguana.
http://help.interfaceware.com/v6/x12-parse-and-generate
In this case the example is parsing a 270 claim and generating a 271 response.
